  6242		It's been a really crazy time here, recollected GreenCoat.
  6243	First I just had a simple assignment to subjugate this town by the Boss.
  6244	It was rather straight forward, infiltrating the city and slowly
  6245	transforming the denizens first into zombie slaves and then into full
  6246	Vampire Fang Troopers.  Of course there was also a rich amount of
  6247	competent fighters to use as Dark Slaves, some people known as Kunou,
  6248	Kodachi, Mousse, Shampoo and possibly the most powerful: Ranma.
  6249	Other converts have been our human agent, Nabiki who basically just wants
  6250	to side with the winners, something I can understand.  And of course
  6251	Gosunkugi, who is know a full fledged Fang Trooper.  Purple's a bit
  6252	wary about him, since he awakened in only one day when it normally takes a
  6253	victim three.  I just think it's because he's been his mental slave for so
  6254	long and deep down the kid actually WANTS to be one of us.  Another thing I
  6255	can relate to as well.
  6256		But it hasn't all been fun and games.  We've been put on a tight
  6257	schedule.  Apparently this is the pivotal city that will enable the Fang to
  6258	full control the nation and then the world.  Of course there has been
  6259	intervention by my and Purple's old "friend", Jo FireWater and the champion 
  6260	good guy known, even to us, only as the Wanderer.  Luckily all of these
  6261	factors as well as the resistance have been taken care of.  Most of the
  6262	resistance fighters have been rounded up.  There are only a few minor loose
  6263	ends to take care of.  Soun is on our side, Tofu has been neutralized and
  6264	the girl, Lotion, (what a babe!  Taihen sure knows how to pick'em), seems
  6265	to hold the key to Purple's detection problems.  He said he'd explain more
  6266	later. 
