  6268	The time for secrecy is over.  It's time for us to take a firm hold
  6269	on this town.  The only thing that can possibly stop us is some outside
  6270	influence.  But that only happens in the funny books.  I think I've been
  6271	working at this too long, I'm beginning to think in plot summaries.+
